	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Your magic came to you seemingly at random. Whether the result of magical experimentation, a gift from a chaotic entity, or even appearing out of nowhere, your magic is chaotic and unpredictable. Some wild mages are spotted at a young age, whereas others discover their volatile magic when they're older. A wild mage's spells always have a chance to do something random. Usually this is a good thing, but accidents do happen.</em></p><p><em>In the world of Elkan, wild magic is the domain of Baphomet, the wild minotaur god.</em></p><table><caption><p>The Wild Mage</p></caption><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\"><p>Level</p></th><th scope=\"col\"><p>Features</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>1</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.yXSOvWE0v2BWMshU]{Random Wild Surge}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>3</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.QqUWmLamy78Eu1dC]{Avert Disaster}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.Cjd9KZdWZd7lum2H]{Voluntary Surge}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>6</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.X04dCtqgA13slfdC]{Delayed Surge}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>10</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.Be3OL8Ulw5y3PAqZ]{Chaos Conductor}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>14</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.TC9Pv4NRHoZ0pYtT]{Magical Blowout}</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table><caption><p>Expanded Spell List</p></caption><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\"><p>Sorcerer Level</p></th><th scope=\"col\"><p>Extra Spells</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>1</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.EBXbuU6UgNza87rc]{Chromatic Orb}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>3</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.gOxZm4XAYTyrlGBo]{Prismatic Bolt}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>5</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.BnfcbtYsHn4lyXML]{Blink}</em></p></td></tr>